---
---

<section class="relative bg-paper-warm py-24 lg:py-32">
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-px bg-rule"></div>

  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="reveal mb-16">
      <h2 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-ink leading-tight">
        Why now
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal-stagger grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <div class="reveal group relative rounded-xl border border-rule/60 bg-white p-8 lg:p-10 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-ink/[0.04] transition-all duration-500">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-teal-soft text-teal flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <circle cx="14" cy="14" r="11"/>
            <path d="M 14 3 c -3 4, -5 8, -5 11 s 2 7, 5 11 M 14 3 c 3 4, 5 8, 5 11 s -2 7, -5 11"/>
            <path d="M 3 14 h 22"/>
            <path d="M 4 9 h 20 M 4 19 h 20"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-2xl font-semibold text-ink mb-4">
          Open data is ready
        </h3>
        <p class="text-slate leading-relaxed">
          France and the EU have invested heavily in public data infrastructure. The raw material for policy assessment exists — it just lacks tooling.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2 -->
      <div class="reveal group relative rounded-xl border border-rule/60 bg-white p-8 lg:p-10 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-ink/[0.04] transition-all duration-500">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-amber-soft text-amber flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path d="M 14 3 L 3 10 v 8 l 11 7 11 -7 v -8 Z"/>
            <path d="M 14 25 v -8 M 3 10 l 11 7 11 -7"/>
            <circle cx="14" cy="12" r="3"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-2xl font-semibold text-ink mb-4">
          AI changed what's possible
        </h3>
        <p class="text-slate leading-relaxed">
          The kind of platform that once required a full engineering department can now be built by a domain expert with the right technical skills and AI-assisted development.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
